    <div class="flex justify-evenly items-center my-6">
      <%= image_tag "car-logo/mercedes-1.svg", class: "w-24 h-24" %>
      <%= image_tag "car-logo/honda-1.svg", class: "w-24 h-24" %>
      <%= image_tag "car-logo/jeep-1.svg", class: "w-24 h-24" %>
      <%= image_tag "car-logo/mini.svg", class: "w-24 h-24" %>
      <%= image_tag "car-logo/ford-1.svg", class: "w-24 h-24" %>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center text-gray-50 my-6">
      <div class="font-bold text-4xl w-1/2">
        <p>Car care, the way we always wanted it to be.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-1/2">
        <p>If a car could ask, this is the system it would ask for. Just great information, communication, and exceptional care. No pushy sales or overpriced crap. Know what you need, what's coming up and what has already been done. Connect direct with the shop, or not. My car loves this!</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
      <%= image_tag "nissan-gt-r-1.jpg", class: "rounded-md h-96" %>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-gray-50 my-6">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-4xl py-3">Car care from the ground up.</h2>
      <p class="py-2">Imagine if the car could tell it's owner when it wasn't feeling well. What if the customer was well informed about the health of their car? What if the shop cared so much for it's customers that it informed them of upcoming services, made it easier to bundle services for discounts, and even made it easier to get estimates?</p>
      <p class="py-2">That is exactly what this system is built to accomplish. A standard and effective POS and shop management system for the shop, that includes training and resources for employees, as well as a service and maintenance app for the customer.</p>
    </div>

    <div id="accordion-collapse" data-accordion="collapse">
      <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-1">
        <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-1">
          <span>What is the Speed Shop Garage?</span>
          <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
            <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="accordion-collapse-body-1" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-1">
        <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900">
          <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Your personal vehicle maintenance application. Own it's own it can help you keep track of the maintenance on your vehicle. When connected to a participating shop, you can get estimates on services, get notifications for up coming or past due services, schedule appointments, chat with service advisors, and much more.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-2">
        <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-2">
          <span>I don't want to be spammed with notification?</span>
          <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
            <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="accordion-collapse-body-2" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-2">
        <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">The app is designed to provide friendly reminders and notifications. It is not trying to sell anything and is not a chat app. More over, you are in control of the frequency and destinations of notifications.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-3">
        <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-3">
          <span>Do I register or will the shop register for me?</span>
          <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
            <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="accordion-collapse-body-3" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-3">
        <div class="p-5 border border-t-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">You can use the app on it's own. Register your account for free and create your garage by adding your vehicle. Input your vehicle information to get started. You may choose to put in your maintenance history or simply use it moving forward. Given the year and the mileage you will see the manufacturers recommended services.</p>
          <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Any participating shop can register you and provide their services. You will be able to see the services they provide and the cost. Schedule appointments with ease or chat with a service advisor to get the exact service you need.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

